# =============================================================================
#
# Emails not arriving?
# 1. Check Railway logs for errors: railway logs
# 2. Verify RESEND_API_KEY is correct (check Resend dashboard)
# 3. Verify BUSINESS_EMAIL is correct
# 4. Check spam folder
# 5. Test API key in Resend dashboard: https://resend.com/logs
